desc_short	-----								Feel the power of flying the AV8B Harrier II. A flight and naval combat simulator with mission planner and fully dynamic open ended campaign. Multi-Player, VR Support and Mod-ability are amongst planned EA updates. Multiple controller support: Flightstick, HOTAS, rudder, MFD panel and gamepad mode.							
